thread.title: Clare Fletcher
thread.title_full: Overflow Cafe reviewed by Clare Fletcher

author: Clare Fletcher
title: Clare Fletcher
text: I've only been with them for 1 month for my personalised greetings cards and gifts site but I'm already happy with the pointers and tips they have given me and have seen a definite increase in traffic so am really happy. I've had the site for 7 years+ and over the years I feel like it's been penalised with google for not being as great as it could. I'm continuing to put in place all of the things they recommended for my site. There's a lot to do and I wish I had more time, but the little things I have changed have already helped. Looking forward to seeing what the next few months can do.
